  {
    "bbox": [
      75,
      1104,
      454,
      1143
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Ta chứng minh : $NC \\perp MD$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      75,
      1163,
      1142,
      1291
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Thật vậy : $\\Delta ADM = \\Delta DCM$ vì $\\hat{A} = \\hat{D} = 90^\\circ$; $AD = DC$; $AM = DN$\n$\\Rightarrow \\widehat{ADM} = \\widehat{DCN}$; mà $\\widehat{ADM} + \\widehat{MDC} = 90^\\circ \\Rightarrow \\widehat{MDC} + \\widehat{DCN} = 90^\\circ \\Rightarrow NC \\perp MD$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      75,
      1317,
      1084,
      1368
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Ta có : $BP \\perp NC (MD // BP)$; $BP \\perp SH \\Rightarrow BP \\perp (SNC) \\Rightarrow (SBP) \\perp (SNC)$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      75,
      1394,
      968,
      1442
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Kẻ $HE \\perp SF \\Rightarrow HE \\perp (SBP) \\Rightarrow d(H, (SBP)) = d(C, (SBP)) = HE$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      75,
      1465,
      833,
      1559
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Do $DC^2 = HC \\cdot NC \\Rightarrow HC = \\frac{DC^2}{NC} = \\frac{2\\sqrt{15}}{5} \\Rightarrow HF = \\frac{\\sqrt{15}}{5}$"
  },
  {
    "bbox": [
      75,
      1581,
      689,
      1672
    ],
    "category": "Text",
    "text": "Mà $HE = \\frac{SH \\cdot HF}{SF} = \\frac{SH \\cdot HF}{\\sqrt{SH^2 + HF^2}} = \\frac{3}{4} = 0,75$"
  },
  {
